Police officers and forensic experts on Wednesday secure evidence at a vehicle accident that occured on the A 100 highway in Berlin, Germany. According to reports a man driving a car caused a series of motorway accidents in Berlin on Tuesday night, injuring six people, three of them seriously, in what German prosecutors have described as an Islamic extremist attack. Photo: AFPNewspaper headline: Gathering evidence  
